## How to use this template

1. Copy this file to the root of your project as `AGENTS.md`
2. Replace `{{PROJECT_NAME}}` with your project name
3. Replace `{{REFERENCE_REPOS}}` with read-only reference repo list (or remove section)
4. Replace `{{BRANDING_RULES}}` with project-specific branding (or remove section)
5. Replace `{{LANGUAGE_CONVENTION}}` with language rules, e.g.:
   - "Code, comments, and commit messages in English"
   - "UI labels and user-facing text in Portuguese (pt-BR)"
6. Commit `AGENTS.md` in the first commit, before any code
7. Delete this "How to use" section from the final file


